## 19. Variable Selection Rationale

**FinalGrade** is selected as the outcome because it directly measures course performance. Variables related to earlier grades, absences, finances, support-service usage, enrollment context, and engagement are retained because they describe student circumstances that may relate to academic performance.

**StudentID** is excluded because it is an identifier. Centering, scaling, and one-hot encoding are not applied on this page because those steps belong in the modeling workflow.

